As a user I can see the current general weather (sunny, rain etc.)

As a user I want to see METAR/ATIS wind measurements (gusts, average wind, directions)

As a user I can see the day and time for the current weather measurement.

As a user I can see the current temperature and humidity.

As a user I want to know barometric pressure

As a user I can follow the weather forecast for the coming days.

As a user I can see the predicted temperature, humidity and wind gusts from the forecast for a certain day and timeframe.

As a user I can also use the application on mobile devices (responsive design).
